com.neovisionaries.bluetooth.ble.util

Enum GattStatusCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GattStatusCode>
      • com.neovisionaries.bluetooth.ble.util.GattStatusCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GattStatusCode>

    public enum GattStatusCode
extends Enum<GattStatusCode>
    This enum represents success code and error codes defined in external/bluetooth/bluedroid/stack/include/gatt_api.h.

    The status parameter in BluetoothGattCallback class is one of the entries in this enum (probably).

    Since:
    1.1
